    "long_instructions": "## Journalist - Level 1: Zero-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice zero-shot prompting through the career of a journalist by giving a simple, unstructured prompt to see how AI responds without any examples or extra details.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a basic prompt like the one below, or a similar one related to breaking news.\r\n\r\n>Summarize the latest news on climate change.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how much detail the AI includes and how clear or vague the summary is.",
